00:15:00.730 --> 00:15:02.230
it needs to be broken down.

00:15:02.230 --> 00:15:04.990
And that gets broken
down by an enzyme.

00:15:04.990 --> 00:15:09.050
And I need a volunteer to help
me demonstrate what's going on.

00:15:09.050 --> 00:15:10.640
