here, what the enzyme does--

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:31.680
come over here.

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:33.620
What the enzyme does is
it breaks the lactose

00:15:33.620 --> 00:15:34.790
into smaller sugars.

00:15:34.790 --> 00:15:38.080
So you can do that
by turning this.

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:38.580
Yeah.

00:15:38.580 --> 00:15:39.705
So that's the way it works.

00:15:39.705 --> 00:15:42.350
