00:40:06.700 --> 00:40:08.200
But what was
interesting about this

00:40:08.200 --> 00:40:09.700
is you know some
of these traits are

00:40:09.700 --> 00:40:11.350
better predictors than others.

00:40:11.350 --> 00:40:13.480
But it's never going to be 100%.

00:40:13.480 --> 00:40:15.640
So you might be right
sort of, you know,

00:40:15.640 --> 00:40:17.590
7, 8, 9 times out of 10.

00:40:17.590 --> 00:40:19.450
But there are some
people that you're not

00:40:19.450 --> 00:40:21.880
going to guess right by
knowing their genetics.

00:40:21.880 --> 00:40:22.480
OK.

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:24.670
I think we just need
to end the suspense

00:40:24.670 --> 00:40:27.045
and see who actually
